# ECG_RECOGNITION_C
1. Project Structure
  ECG_RECOGNITION_C/
  ├── CMakeLists.txt
  ├── main.c
  ├── test.c
# Conv weight files
  ├── conv1_bias.txt
  ├── conv1_weight.txt
 # PartialConv
  ├── conv2_bias.txt
  ├── conv2_weight.txt
  ├── conv3_bias.txt
  ├── conv3_weight.txt
 # DepthwiseConv
  ├── conv4_bias.txt     
  ├── conv4_weight.txt  
  # PointwiseConv
  ├── conv5_bias.txt    
  ├── conv5_weight.txt
# FC weight files
  ├── fc1_bias.txt
  ├── fc1_weight.txt
  ├── fc2_bias.txt
  ├── fc2_weight.txt
# Test ECG data
  ├── X_test_np.txt
  ├── Y_test_np.txt
  └── cmake-build-debug/

2. Environment Requirements
Before running this project, make sure the following environment is set up:
Operating System: Windows
Compiler: GCC / MinGW-w64 or Visual Studio C/C++ Build Tools
Build Tool: CMake
Editor (optional): VS Code

3. Run the Project
3.1 Method 1: Run the executable directly in the terminal: .\main.exe
3.2 Method 2: Rebuild and Run
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
cmake --build .
.\main.exe
